criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Women in the postmenopausal period (menopausal for at least one year, confirmed by
             laboratory diagnostic tests menopause - LH and high FSH and estradiol decreased);

          -  Healthy;

          -  Who agree to participate and sign the consent term.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  The one who does not provide the necessary information for the development of the
             study;

          -  Present orthopedic limitations;

          -  Patients with previously diagnosed and treatment of diseases such as type II diabetes
             mellitus, hypertension and cardiovascular disease.
